					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It can't cross more than 1 page.  "Crossing a page" means when you add an 8-bit value to a 16-bit value, it needs to change the high byte of the 16-bit value.  The only time you see crossing a page penalties is in the instructions that add X or Y to an address, or the branch instructions.</div>

					
